{
  "video_id": "weWl6PqAdHY",
  "title": "A celebration of natural hair | Cheyenne Cochrane",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12621.0,
      "end_time": 15436.0,
      "text": "I am from the South Side of Chicago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15460.0,
      "end_time": 19556.0,
      "text": "and in seventh grade, I had a best friend named Jenny"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19580.0,
      "end_time": 22380.0,
      "text": "who lived on the Southwest Side of Chicago."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23180.0,
      "end_time": 25156.0,
      "text": "Jenny was white,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25180.0,
      "end_time": 29156.0,
      "text": "and if you know anything about the segregated demographics of Chicago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29180.0,
      "end_time": 32316.0,
      "text": "you know that there are not too many black people"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32340.000000000004,
      "end_time": 34396.0,
      "text": "who live on the Southwest Side of Chicago."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34420.0,
      "end_time": 35676.0,
      "text": "But Jenny was my girl"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35700.0,
      "end_time": 40596.0,
      "text": "and so we would hang out every so often after school and on the weekends."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40620.0,
      "end_time": 43915.0,
      "text": "And so one day we were hanging out in her living room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43939.0,
      "end_time": 47196.0,
      "text": "talking about 13-year-old things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47220.0,
      "end_time": 50436.0,
      "text": "and Jenny&#39;s little sister Rosie was in the room with us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50460.0,
      "end_time": 53516.0,
      "text": "and she was sitting behind me just kind of playing in my hair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53540.0,
      "end_time": 57620.0,
      "text": "and I wasn&#39;t thinking too much about what she was doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58220.0,
      "end_time": 60436.0,
      "text": "But at a pause in the conversation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60460.0,
      "end_time": 62956.0,
      "text": "Rosie tapped me on the shoulder."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62980.0,
      "end_time": 65340.0,
      "text": "She said, \"Can I ask you a question?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65940.0,
      "end_time": 67700.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Yeah, Rosie. Sure.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68620.0,
      "end_time": 70360.0,
      "text": "\"Are you black?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70600.0,
      "end_time": 72276.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72300.0,
      "end_time": 74196.0,
      "text": "The room froze."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74220.0,
      "end_time": 75420.0,
      "text": "Silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76699.0,
      "end_time": 78956.0,
      "text": "Jenny and Rosie&#39;s mom was not too far away."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78980.0,
      "end_time": 81876.0,
      "text": "She was in the kitchen and she overheard the conversation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 81900.0,
      "end_time": 83420.0,
      "text": "and she was mortified."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 84140.0,
      "end_time": 87700.0,
      "text": "She said, \"Rosie! You can&#39;t ask people questions like that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88460.0,
      "end_time": 92350.0,
      "text": "And Jenny was my friend, and I know she was really embarrassed."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92600.0,
      "end_time": 96396.0,
      "text": "I felt kind of bad for her, but actually I was not offended."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96420.0,
      "end_time": 101476.0,
      "text": "I figured it wasn&#39;t Rosie&#39;s fault that in her 10 short years on this earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101500.0,
      "end_time": 103956.0,
      "text": "living on the Southwest Side of Chicago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103980.0,
      "end_time": 106860.0,
      "text": "she wasn&#39;t 100 percent sure what a black person looked like."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 107260.0,
      "end_time": 108676.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s fair."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108700.0,
      "end_time": 111760.0,
      "text": "But what was more surprising to me was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111100.0,
      "end_time": 115595.0,
      "text": "in all of this time I had spent with Jenny and Rosie&#39;s family --"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115620.0,
      "end_time": 116956.0,
      "text": "hanging out with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116980.0,
      "end_time": 118236.0,
      "text": "playing with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 121360.0,
      "text": "even physically interacting with them --"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121600.0,
      "end_time": 125556.0,
      "text": "it was not until Rosie put her hands in my hair"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 125580.0,
      "end_time": 128100.0,
      "text": "that she thought to ask me if I was black."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 129380.0,
      "end_time": 132760.0,
      "text": "That was the first time I would realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 132100.0,
      "end_time": 137360.0,
      "text": "how big of a role the texture of my hair played in confirming my ethnicity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137600.0,
      "end_time": 141660.0,
      "text": "but also that it would play a key role in how I&#39;m viewed by others in society."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 143220.0,
      "end_time": 146436.0,
      "text": "Garrett A. Morgan and Madame CJ Walker were pioneers"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 146460.0,
      "end_time": 149980.0,
      "text": "of the black hair-care and beauty industry in the early 1900s."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150500.0,
      "end_time": 154276.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re best known as the inventors of chemically-based hair creams"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 154300.0,
      "end_time": 155836.0,
      "text": "and heat straightening tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 155860.0,
      "end_time": 159436.0,
      "text": "designed to permanently, or semipermanently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 159460.0,
      "end_time": 162100.0,
      "text": "alter the texture of black hair."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 163180.0,
      "end_time": 166956.0,
      "text": "Oftentimes when we think about the history of blacks in America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 166980.0,
      "end_time": 169875.0,
      "text": "we think about the heinous acts"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 169900.0,
      "end_time": 174396.0,
      "text": "and numerous injustices that we experienced as people of color"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 174420.0,
      "end_time": 176155.0,
      "text": "because of the color of our skin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 176180.0,
      "end_time": 179836.0,
      "text": "when in fact, in post-Civil War America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 179860.0,
      "end_time": 185360.0,
      "text": "it was the hair of an African-American male or female"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 185600.0,
      "end_time": 189916.0,
      "text": "that was known as the most \"telling feature\" of Negro status,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 189940.0,
      "end_time": 191859.0,
      "text": "more so than the color of the skin."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 192940.0,
      "end_time": 195276.0,
      "text": "And so before they were staples"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 195300.0,
      "end_time": 199236.0,
      "text": "of the multibillion-dollar hair-care industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 202360.0,
      "text": "our dependency on tools and products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 202600.0,
      "end_time": 205356.0,
      "text": "like the hair relaxer and the pressing comb,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 205380.0,
      "end_time": 209796.0,
      "text": "were more about our survival and advancement as a race"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 209820.0,
      "end_time": 212190.0,
      "text": "in postslavery America."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 213700.0,
      "end_time": 217760.0,
      "text": "Over the years, we grew accustomed to this idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 217100.0,
      "end_time": 222220.0,
      "text": "that straighter and longer hair meant better and more beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 223620.0,
      "end_time": 226756.0,
      "text": "We became culturally obsessed"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 226780.0,
      "end_time": 229980.0,
      "text": "with this idea of having what we like to call ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 230660.0,
      "end_time": 231859.0,
      "text": "\"good hair.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 233500.0,
      "end_time": 235760.0,
      "text": "This essentially means:"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 235100.0,
      "end_time": 238660.0,
      "text": "the looser the curl pattern, the better the hair."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 239540.0,
      "end_time": 245995.0,
      "text": "And we let these institutionalized ideas form a false sense of hierarchy"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 246200.0,
      "end_time": 251596.0,
      "text": "that would determine what was considered a good grade of hair"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 251620.0,
      "end_time": 252980.0,
      "text": "and what was not."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 255140.0,
      "end_time": 258435.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s worse is that we let these false ideologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 258459.0,
      "end_time": 261195.0,
      "text": "invade our perception of ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 261220.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264556.0,
      "text": "and they still continue to infect our cultural identity"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 264580.0,
      "end_time": 267200.0,
      "text": "as African-American women today."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 268540.0,
      "end_time": 270360.0,
      "text": "So what did we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 270600.0,
      "end_time": 274760.0,
      "text": "We went to the hair salon every six to eight weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 274100.0,
      "end_time": 275476.0,
      "text": "without fail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 275500.0,
      "end_time": 278836.0,
      "text": "to subject our scalps to harsh straightening chemicals"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 278860.0,
      "end_time": 280796.0,
      "text": "beginning at a very young age --"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 280820.0,
      "end_time": 282876.0,
      "text": "sometimes eight, 10 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 282900.0,
      "end_time": 286116.0,
      "text": "that would result in hair loss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 286140.0,
      "end_time": 287356.0,
      "text": "bald spots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 287380.0,
      "end_time": 289580.0,
      "text": "sometimes even burns on the scalp."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 295360.0,
      "text": "We fry our hair at temperatures of 450 degrees Fahrenheit or higher"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 295600.0,
      "end_time": 296316.0,
      "text": "almost daily,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 296340.0,
      "end_time": 298340.0,
      "text": "to maintain the straight look."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 304156.0,
      "text": "Or we simply cover our hair up with wigs and weaves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 304180.0,
      "end_time": 306836.0,
      "text": "only to let our roots breathe in private"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 306860.0,
      "end_time": 309980.0,
      "text": "where no one knows what&#39;s really going on under there."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 311340.0,
      "end_time": 314635.0,
      "text": "We adopted these practices in our own communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 314660.0,
      "end_time": 319996.0,
      "text": "and so it&#39;s no wonder why today the typical ideal vision"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 320200.0,
      "end_time": 322756.0,
      "text": "of a professional black woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 322780.0,
      "end_time": 324676.0,
      "text": "especially in corporate America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 324700.0,
      "end_time": 327200.0,
      "text": "tends to look like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 328140.0,
      "end_time": 329700.0,
      "text": "rather than like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 330980.0,
      "end_time": 333980.0,
      "text": "And she certainly doesn&#39;t look like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 335140.0,
      "end_time": 337116.0,
      "text": "In September of this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 337140.0,
      "end_time": 339635.0,
      "text": "a federal court ruled it lawful"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 339660.0,
      "end_time": 343996.0,
      "text": "for a company to discriminate against hiring an employee"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 344200.0,
      "end_time": 347990.0,
      "text": "based on if she or he wears dreadlocks."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 348380.0,
      "end_time": 349596.0,
      "text": "In the case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 349620.0,
      "end_time": 351876.0,
      "text": "the hiring manager in Mobile, Alabama"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 351900.0,
      "end_time": 353620.0,
      "text": "is on record as saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 354780.0,
      "end_time": 356619.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m not saying yours are messy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 357460.0,
      "end_time": 358796.0,
      "text": "but ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 358820.0,
      "end_time": 360392.0,
      "text": "you know what I&#39;m talking about.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 362260.0,
      "end_time": 364500.0,
      "text": "Well, what was she talking about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 365580.0,
      "end_time": 367300.0,
      "text": "Did she think that they were ugly?"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 368740.0,
      "end_time": 373196.0,
      "text": "Or maybe they were just a little too Afrocentric"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 373220.0,
      "end_time": 375500.0,
      "text": "and pro-black-looking for her taste."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 376300.0,
      "end_time": 378236.0,
      "text": "Or maybe it&#39;s not about Afrocentricity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 378260.0,
      "end_time": 380796.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s more just about it being a little too \"urban\""
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 380820.0,
      "end_time": 382219.0,
      "text": "for the professional setting."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 383700.0,
      "end_time": 387356.0,
      "text": "Perhaps she had a genuine concern in that they looked \"scary\""
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 387380.0,
      "end_time": 390900.0,
      "text": "and that they would intimidate the clients and their customer base."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 392500.0,
      "end_time": 397596.0,
      "text": "All of these words are ones that are too often associated"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 397620.0,
      "end_time": 401600.0,
      "text": "with the stigma attached to natural hairstyles."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 401820.0,
      "end_time": 403200.0,
      "text": "And this ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 403540.0,
      "end_time": 405500.0,
      "text": "this has got to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 407100.0,
      "end_time": 408356.0,
      "text": "In 2013,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 408380.0,
      "end_time": 412876.0,
      "text": "a white paper published by the Deloitte Leadership Center for Inclusion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 412900.0,
      "end_time": 416316.0,
      "text": "studied 3,000 individuals in executive leadership roles"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 416340.0,
      "end_time": 418955.0,
      "text": "on the concept of covering in the workplace"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 418980.0,
      "end_time": 423600.0,
      "text": "based on appearance, advocacy, affiliation and association."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 424140.0,
      "end_time": 427195.0,
      "text": "When thinking about appearance-based covering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 427220.0,
      "end_time": 428476.0,
      "text": "the study showed"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 428500.0,
      "end_time": 434556.0,
      "text": "that 67 percent of women of color cover in the workplace"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 434580.0,
      "end_time": 435859.0,
      "text": "based on their appearance."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 437180.0,
      "end_time": 441636.0,
      "text": "Of the total respondents who admitted to appearance-based covering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 441660.0,
      "end_time": 445916.0,
      "text": "82 percent said that it was somewhat to extremely important"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 445940.0,
      "end_time": 448940.0,
      "text": "for them to do so for their professional advancement."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 449620.0,
      "end_time": 451860.0,
      "text": "Now, this is Ursula Burns."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 452940.0,
      "end_time": 458476.0,
      "text": "She is the first African-American female CEO of a Fortune 500 company --"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 458500.0,
      "end_time": 459700.0,
      "text": "of Xerox."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 460180.0,
      "end_time": 462236.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s known by her signature look,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 462260.0,
      "end_time": 463956.0,
      "text": "the one that you see here."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 463980.0,
      "end_time": 468260.0,
      "text": "A short, nicely trimmed, well-manicured Afro."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 469180.0,
      "end_time": 472260.0,
      "text": "Ms. Burns is what we like to call a \"natural girl.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 473220.0,
      "end_time": 476436.0,
      "text": "And she is paving the way and showing what&#39;s possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 476460.0,
      "end_time": 480195.0,
      "text": "for African-American women seeking to climb the corporate ladder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 480220.0,
      "end_time": 483600.0,
      "text": "but still wishing to wear natural hairstyles."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 483740.0,
      "end_time": 487796.0,
      "text": "But today the majority of African-American women"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 487820.0,
      "end_time": 492516.0,
      "text": "who we still look to as leaders, icons and role models,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 492540.0,
      "end_time": 495836.0,
      "text": "still opt for a straight-hair look."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 495860.0,
      "end_time": 497760.0,
      "text": "Now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 497100.0,
      "end_time": 498796.0,
      "text": "maybe it&#39;s because they want to --"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 498820.0,
      "end_time": 502116.0,
      "text": "this is authentically how they feel best --"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 502140.0,
      "end_time": 503635.0,
      "text": "but maybe --"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 503660.0,
      "end_time": 505276.0,
      "text": "and I bet --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 505300.0,
      "end_time": 508556.0,
      "text": "a part of them felt like they had to"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 508580.0,
      "end_time": 513590.0,
      "text": "in order to reach the level of success that they have attained today."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 514260.0,
      "end_time": 519356.0,
      "text": "There is a natural hair movement that is sweeping the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 519380.0,
      "end_time": 521659.0,
      "text": "and also in some places in Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 522580.00000000006,
      "end_time": 527676.0,
      "text": "Millions of women are exploring what it means to transition to natural hair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 527700.0,
      "end_time": 531715.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re cutting off years and years of dry, damaged ends"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 531739.0,
      "end_time": 533931.0,
      "text": "in order to restore their natural curl pattern."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 534739.0,
      "end_time": 539760.0,
      "text": "I know because I have been an advocate and an ambassador for this movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 539100.0,
      "end_time": 540900.0,
      "text": "for roughly the last three years."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 541620.0,
      "end_time": 547196.0,
      "text": "After 27 years of excessive heat and harsh chemicals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 547220.0,
      "end_time": 552700.0,
      "text": "my hair was beginning to show extreme signs of wear and tear."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 553300.0,
      "end_time": 554835.0,
      "text": "It was breaking off,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 554860.0,
      "end_time": 556236.0,
      "text": "it was thinning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 556260.0,
      "end_time": 559316.0,
      "text": "looking just extremely dry and brittle."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 559340.0,
      "end_time": 562716.0,
      "text": "All those years of chasing that conventional image of beauty"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 562740.0,
      "end_time": 563956.0,
      "text": "that we saw earlier"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 563980.0,
      "end_time": 565940.0,
      "text": "was finally beginning to take its toll."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 567620.0,
      "end_time": 569836.0,
      "text": "I wanted to do something about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 569860.0,
      "end_time": 574356.0,
      "text": "and so I started what I called the \"No Heat Challenge,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 574380.0,
      "end_time": 578236.0,
      "text": "where I would refrain from using heat styling tools on my hair"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 578260.0,
      "end_time": 579540.0,
      "text": "for six months."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 580780.0,
      "end_time": 583596.0,
      "text": "And like a good millennial,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 583620.0,
      "end_time": 585836.0,
      "text": "I documented it on social media."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 585860.0,
      "end_time": 587116.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 587140.0,
      "end_time": 591196.0,
      "text": "I documented as I reluctantly cut off"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 591220.0,
      "end_time": 594980.0,
      "text": "three to four inches of my beloved hair."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 595860.0,
      "end_time": 601396.0,
      "text": "I documented as I struggled to master these natural hairstyles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 601420.0,
      "end_time": 605435.0,
      "text": "and also as I struggled to embrace them"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 605460.0,
      "end_time": 608700.0,
      "text": "and think that they actually looked good."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 609580.0,
      "end_time": 615600.0,
      "text": "And I documented as my hair texture slowly began to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 616260.0,
      "end_time": 618716.0,
      "text": "By sharing this journey openly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 618740.0,
      "end_time": 622516.0,
      "text": "I learned that I was not the only woman going through this"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 622540.0,
      "end_time": 626315.0,
      "text": "and that in fact there were thousands and thousands of other women"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 626340.0,
      "end_time": 628600.0,
      "text": "who were longing to do the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 628780.0,
      "end_time": 631116.0,
      "text": "So they would reach out to me and they would say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 631140.0,
      "end_time": 633396.0,
      "text": "\"Cheyenne, how did you do that natural hairstyle"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 633420.0,
      "end_time": 635356.0,
      "text": "that I saw you with the other day?"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 635380.0,
      "end_time": 637396.0,
      "text": "What new products have you started using"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 637420.0,
      "end_time": 639756.0,
      "text": "that might be a little better for my hair texture"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 639780.0,
      "end_time": 641220.0,
      "text": "as it begins to change?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 641780.0,
      "end_time": 645596.0,
      "text": "Or, \"What are some of the natural hair routines"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 645620.0,
      "end_time": 649740.0,
      "text": "that I should begin to adopt to slowly restore the health of my hair?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 650980.0,
      "end_time": 654676.0,
      "text": "But I also found that there were a large number of women"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 654700.0,
      "end_time": 658500.0,
      "text": "who were extremely hesitant to take that first step"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 659540.0,
      "end_time": 662600.0,
      "text": "because they were paralyzed by fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 663220.0,
      "end_time": 664956.0,
      "text": "Fear of the unknown --"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 664980.0,
      "end_time": 666580.0,
      "text": "what would they now look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 667260.0,
      "end_time": 671596.0,
      "text": "How would they feel about themselves with these natural hairstyles?"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 671620.0,
      "end_time": 674360.0,
      "text": "And most importantly to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 674600.0,
      "end_time": 676600.0,
      "text": "how would others view them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 677220.0,
      "end_time": 679360.0,
      "text": "Over the last three years"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 679600.0,
      "end_time": 682955.0,
      "text": "of having numerous conversations with friends of mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 682980.0,
      "end_time": 686916.0,
      "text": "and also complete strangers from around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 686940.0,
      "end_time": 689636.0,
      "text": "I learned some really important things"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 689660.0,
      "end_time": 693380.0,
      "text": "about how African-American women identify with their hair."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 694620.0,
      "end_time": 696596.0,
      "text": "And so when I think back"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 696620.0,
      "end_time": 700156.0,
      "text": "to that hiring manager in Mobile, Alabama,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 700180.0,
      "end_time": 702915.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d say, \"Actually, no."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 702940.0,
      "end_time": 705396.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t know what you&#39;re talking about.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 705420.0,
      "end_time": 707380.0,
      "text": "But here are some things that we do know."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 708540.0,
      "end_time": 713516.0,
      "text": "We know that when black women embrace their love for their natural hair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 713540.0,
      "end_time": 716996.0,
      "text": "it helps to undo generations of teaching"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 717200.0,
      "end_time": 720316.0,
      "text": "that black in its natural state is not beautiful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 720340.0,
      "end_time": 723260.0,
      "text": "or something to be hidden or covered up."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 724300.0,
      "end_time": 728555.0,
      "text": "We know that black women express their individuality"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 728580.0,
      "end_time": 731676.0,
      "text": "and experience feelings of empowerment"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 731700.0,
      "end_time": 735740.0,
      "text": "by experimenting with different hairstyles regularly."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 736700.0,
      "end_time": 738316.0,
      "text": "And we also know"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 738340.0,
      "end_time": 743236.0,
      "text": "that when we&#39;re invited to wear our natural hair in the workplace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 743260.0,
      "end_time": 746636.0,
      "text": "it reinforces that we are uniquely valued"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 746660.0,
      "end_time": 750420.0,
      "text": "and thus helps us to flourish and advance professionally."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 752340.0,
      "end_time": 753540.0,
      "text": "I leave you with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 754420.0,
      "end_time": 757339.0,
      "text": "In a time of racial and social tension,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 758260.0,
      "end_time": 760196.0,
      "text": "embracing this movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 760220.0,
      "end_time": 761996.0,
      "text": "and others like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 762200.0,
      "end_time": 765540.0,
      "text": "help us to rise above the confines of the status quo."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 766540.0,
      "end_time": 772596.0,
      "text": "So when you see a woman with braids or locks draping down her back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 772620.0,
      "end_time": 775156.0,
      "text": "or you notice your colleague"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 775180.0,
      "end_time": 778260.0,
      "text": "who has stopped straightening her hair to work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 779180.0,
      "end_time": 782756.0,
      "text": "do not simply approach her and admire"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 782780.0,
      "end_time": 785596.0,
      "text": "and ask her if you can touch it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 785620.0,
      "end_time": 786876.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 786900.0,
      "end_time": 788740.0,
      "text": "Really appreciate her."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 789740.0,
      "end_time": 790956.0,
      "text": "Applaud her."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 790980.0,
      "end_time": 794700.0,
      "text": "Heck, even high-five her if that&#39;s what you feel so inclined to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 795340.0,
      "end_time": 796916.0,
      "text": "Because this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 796940.0,
      "end_time": 799700.0,
      "text": "this is more than about a hairstyle."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 800700.0,
      "end_time": 803620.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about self-love and self-worth."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 804420.0,
      "end_time": 806636.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about being brave enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 806660.0,
      "end_time": 810699.0,
      "text": "not to fold under the pressure of others&#39; expectations."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 811620.0,
      "end_time": 816196.0,
      "text": "And about knowing that making the decision to stray from the norm"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 816220.0,
      "end_time": 818676.0,
      "text": "does not define who we are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 818700.0,
      "end_time": 821200.0,
      "text": "but it simply reveals who we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 821860.0,
      "end_time": 823596.0,
      "text": "And finally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 823620.0,
      "end_time": 825476.0,
      "text": "being brave is easier"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 825500.0,
      "end_time": 827940.0,
      "text": "when we can count on the compassion of others."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 828500.0,
      "end_time": 830356.0,
      "text": "So after today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 830380.0,
      "end_time": 833700.0,
      "text": "I certainly hope that we can count on you."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 834180.0,
      "end_time": 835396.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 835420.0,
      "end_time": 839472.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}